summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department and making appropriations for the completion of payments on existing real estate contracts for the purchase of certain property in Sections 4 and 5, Township 27 North, Range 16 East, W.M. (Chelan County, Washington), and Sections 19, 20, 29 and 30, Township 28 North, Range 16 East, W.M. (Chelan County, Washington) for land to exchange for Forest Service property in the Cedar River Watershed.
